===Shipyard=== Location of your ships when they are not out at sea. At higher Sailing levels, can increased the number of ships one commands.
===Hulls and Plating=== The interior wood of your ship's hull. The metal plating applied to the wood to increase the hull integrity.
===Chest and lootcrates=== Storage of items, at higher levels can increase the quantity/quality of loot the ship returns back to port.
===Figurehead=== Increase the morale of your ship's crew members
===Cannons=== Increase the combat strength of your ship
